name: Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove
desc: During your Main Phase: You can Special Summon 1 "Zubaba" monster or "Gagaga" monster from your hand. If you control a "Gogogo" monster or "Dododo" monster, except "Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove", while this card is in your GY: You can Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field. You can only us each effect of "Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove" once per turn.
